:: Start {"position":"300,200","size":"100,100"}
You wake — or perhaps you sleep. The air smells of dust.

This is the [[Somni Library->Room]], a place out of time, born from unconsciousness. Your psyche is trapped here in a small study room — and it will stay trapped until you find a way out.


:: StartPage {"position":"175,200","size":"100,100"}
<div class="start-screen">
	<div class="title">SOMNI LIBRARY</div>

	<div class="menu">
		[[START GAME ->Start]]
	</div>
</div>


:: WordBox {"position":"550,325","size":"100,100"}
A box with several compartments, like an armoire. On the top of it is a grid of seemingly unrelated letters. On closer inspection it appears the columns and rows can be rotated to form five-letter words.

The email mentioned three names — //Robert//, //Martin//, //Cecil//. Perhaps those names are the words hidden in this grid?


Names found (separate with commas): <<textbox "$wbInput" "" autofocus>>

<<button "Submit">>
  <<if $wbInput.toUpperCase().includes("ROBERT") and $wbInput.toUpperCase().includes("MARTIN") and $wbInput.toUpperCase().includes("CECIL")>>
    <<set $wordBoxSolved to true>>
    <<set $hasLibrarianC to true>>
    <<goto "WordBoxSolved">>
  <<else>>
    Those aren't the right names — keep looking.
  <</if>>
<</button>>

<<if $wordBoxSolved>>
The box is open. Figurine C rests in your hands.
<</if>>

[[← Go back->Room]]


:: WordBoxSolved {"position":"675,325","size":"100,100"}
The box clicks open! Inside, nestled in velvet, is Figurine C.

''✦ You acquired Librarian C!''

Now the figurine puzzle can be solved.

[[Go to the librarian figurines ->Librarians]] | [[← Go back to room->Room]]


:: StoryStylesheet [stylesheet]
body {
  background-color: #0b0b0d;
  color: #d8d2c4;
  font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
  font-size: 22px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

#passages {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

#ui-bar {
  display: none;
}

#passages {
  animation: fadein 1s ease;
}

.start-screen {
  width: 100vw;
  min-height: 100vh;

  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;

  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;

  background-image:url("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sia0930/INSOMNIA_LIBRARY/Resource/SomniLibraryBackground.png");
  background-size:cover;
  background-position:center;
  background-repeat:no-repeat;
}

.title {
  font-size: 56px;
  letter-spacing: 6px;
  color: white;
  text-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}

.menu {
  margin-top: 40px;
}

.menu a {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 12px 30px;
  margin: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #888;
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #ccc;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.menu a:hover {
  background-color: #444;
  color: white;
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.ending{
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 80px auto;
  margin-top: 20px;
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: #ddd;
    
  animation: fadein 2s ease;
}

.ending-menu{
  margin-top: 60px;
}

.ending-menu a{
  padding: 8px 20px;
  border: 1px solid #666;
  color: #ccc;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.ending-menu a:hover{
  background-color: #333;
  color: white;
}
.ending .glow{
  color: white;
  font-size: 20px;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 25px #5d1e69;
}

.ending strong{
  color: white;
  font-size: 22px;
  text-shadow:
    0 0 10px #5d1e69,
    0 0 25px #25092A,
    0 0 40px #25092A;
}

@keyframes fadein {
from { opacity: 0; }
to { opacity: 1; }
}
